title: Goodell, owners expect future vote on LA relocation
text:
> Sports Goodell, owners expect future vote on LA relocation Dallas Cowboys owner Jerry Jones, and his daughter Charlotte Jones, confer during a break of the National Football League owners meeting, in New York, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015. The owners are considering the desire of three franchises — the St. Louis Rams, Oakland Raiders and San Diego Chargers — to move to Los Angeles.(AP Photo/Richard Drew)
